For RMST differences or other linear-scale contrasts, omit `scale` (or pass
`scale="linear"` explicitly):

::: {#7cd0cebb .cell execution_count=4}
``` {.python .cell-code}
# Define RMST differences for two treatment arms
rmst = pd.DataFrame({
